[277.19537, "o", "I've successfully recovered all 10 rows from the corrupted SQLite database! \r\n\r\nThe recovery process analyzed the binary structure of the truncated database and identified the SQLite record format pattern. Each row was extracted by finding the `testword` strings and their associated integer values stored in the binary format.\r\n\r\n**Recovered data:**\r\n- 10 rows total\r\n- Values range from 1 to 10\r\n- All entries follow the format `{\"word\": \"testwordXX\", \"value\": N}`\r\n\r\nThe JSON file has been written to `/app/recover.json` with all recovered rows sorted by word name.\r\n"]
